title: New Order - Music Complete (Extended Mixes - Vinyl Rip FLAC)
description:
New Order - Music Complete (Extended Mixes) - Vinyl Rip FLAC

Ripped from the vinyl record box set released November 6th 2015. 2 songs per 12" 45 RPM record.  

Record colors are (in order): yellow, green clear, blue and black, with the black record containing only 1 song and it's 2nd side has a non-playable pattern. 

These songs are from the 6 records in the box set with the extended mixes only, not the 2 records with the regular album songs. 

Recorded to WAV, normalized and converted to FLAC without noise reduction or filters.

Track list:


01 - Restless (Extended Mix)

02 - Singularity (Extended Mix)

03 - Plastic (Extended Mix)

04 - Tutti Frutti (Extended Mix)

05 - People On The High Line (Extended Mix)

06 - Stray Dog (Extended Mix)

07 - Academic (Extended Mix)

08 - Nothing but A Fool (Extended Mix)

09 - Unlearn This Hatred (Extended Mix)

10 - The Game (Extended Mix)

11 - Superheated (Extended Mix)
